name: AlphabetChuChuTrain
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: chu chu train
des:
Alphabet Chu Chu Train is fun and engaging skill for kids that will take chu chu train to different stations and teach alphabet letters along with alphabet song.
It provides awesome sound effects for each word and reads the spelling as well.
The skill remembers your last state and continues from that state when you invoke next time. 
Enjoy the fun ride!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
